caption.paragraph:
FIGURE 31.

Laferollaeus angustissimus


gen. et sp. nov.

, orig. A–I: holotype, male and J: paratype, female from QLD (“… Cape Tribulation area…”); 
A
: body, dorsal; 
B
: head, dorsal; 
C
: head, ventral; 
D
: thorax, ventral; 
E
: lateral side of abdominal segments 5 and 6, dorsal; 
F
: male anal sclerite, ventral; 
G
: tegmen, ventral; 
H
: penis trunk, dorsal; 
I
: proximal part of inner sac with armature; 
J
: ovipositor, ventral. Scale bars: 
a
= 1.0 mm to Fig. A; 
b
= 0.5 mm to Figs B–E; 
с
= 0.25 mm to Figs F–J.
